snippet: Venezuela’s top diplomat in Nairobi was killed at her home by three intruders over a power struggle at the embassy, the Kenyan police said Tuesday.
abstract: Olga Fonseca Gimenez, Venezuela's top diplomat in Nairobi, Kenya, is killed at her home by three intruders; police say the murder is connected to a power struggle at the embassy.
lead_paragraph: Venezuela’s top diplomat in Nairobi was killed at her home by three intruders over a power struggle at the embassy, the Kenyan police said Tuesday.

headline.main: Kenya: Venezuelan Diplomat Killed in Embassy Feud, Police Say
headline.print_headline: Kenya: Venezuelan Diplomat Killed in Embassy Feud, Police Say
